<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLenczowski1990"><a href="/wiki/George_Lenczowski" title="George Lenczowski">Lenczowski, George</a> (1990). <i>American Presidents and the Middle East</i>. <a href="/wiki/Duke_University_Press" title="Duke University Press">Duke University Press</a>. pp.&#160;130. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0822309726" class="internal">ISBN 0-8223-0972-6</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=American+Presidents+and+the+Middle+East&amp;rft.aulast=Lenczowski&amp;rft.aufirst=George&amp;rft.au=Lenczowski%2C+George&amp;rft.date=1990&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B130&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BDuke+University+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=0-8223-0972-6&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:1973_oil_crisis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/oil/" class="external text" title="http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/oil/" rel="nofollow">"The price of oil - in context"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/oil/" class="external free" title="http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/oil/" rel="nofollow">http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/oil/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-05-29</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+price+of+oil+-+in+context&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fbackground%2Foil%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:1973_oil_crisis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> The Power of Oil: The Arab Oil Weapon and the Netherlands, the United Kingdom, Canada, Japan, and the United States Roy Licklider International Studies Quarterly, Vol. 32, No. 2 (Jun., 1988), pp. 206.</li>
