<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> The Power of Oil: The Arab Oil Weapon and the Netherlands, the United Kingdom, Canada, Japan, and the United States Roy Licklider International Studies Quarterly, Vol. 32, No. 2 (Jun., 1988), pp. 217.</li>
