<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> Oil and the Macroeconomy since the 1970s Robert B. Barsky and Lutz Kilian The Journal of Economic Perspectives, Vol. 18, No. 4 (Autumn, 2004), pp. 115.</li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> The Irony of State Strength: Comparative Responses to the Oil Shocks in the 1970s G. John Ikenberry International Organization, Vol. 40, No. 1 (Winter, 1986), pp. 107.</li>
